> doubles every 7.2 years or so.
>
> This year, I started actively investing as an LP (Limited Partner) in two
> funds for bootstrappers. This will get its own full newsletter article
> shortly, but basically my idea is that since I was lucky enough to have a
> pretty privileged life which certainly helped me start and do well with m=
y
> work, if I can pay it forward and help other bootstrappers get started wi=
