>
> Currently, the bulk of my income is varied. It=E2=80=99s broken up betwee=
n
> software, courses, books, passive investments and podcasting - although i=
t
> mostly leans towards my one software company.
>
> Yes, it seems like it=E2=80=99d be more work to have such varied sources =
